high_descs: Go toward the door, turn right, go toward the refrigerator, turn left, go toward the oven, turn right, and go to the sink.
Take the large knife from the counter next to the sink.
Turn around and go to the tomato on the counter.
Slice the tomato on the counter.
Turn left, go toward the wall, turn left, and go to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, put the knife in the refrigerator, and close the refrigerator.
Turn left, go to the microwave, turn left, and go to the tomato on the counter.
Take a slice of tomato from the counter.
Turn around, go to the microwave, and turn left.
Open the microwave, put the tomato in the microwave, close the microwave, run the microwave for two seconds, open the microwave, take the tomato from the microwave, and close the microwave.
Turn around, go to the refrigerator, and turn left.
Open the refrigerator, put the tomato in the refrigerator, and close the refrigerator.

Cut the tomato on the counter into slices.
Turn around and walk forward to face the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge on the bottom shelf beside the cup.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the tomato on the counter.
Pick up a slice of tomato on the counter.
Turn to the right and walk over to face the microwave.
Heat the tomato slice in the microwave.
Turn around and walk forward and turn to the left to face the fridge.
Place the tomato slice in freezer on the top shelf.
